modules
mongodb(without schema)
    interact with mongodb database without (schema =>rules & regulations).

mongoose(with schema)
    interact with mongodb database with schema.

oradb 
    connect with oracle database

JWT -simple 
    token based 


Note : above module downloads to "node_modules" folded in current path



Software installations
----------------------
1) Download and install NodeJS
    website: https://nodejs.org/en/download/

2)  install yarn tool
    > npm install -g yarn
    -g stands for global installation

3) download and install VisualStudioCode
    website: https://code.visualstudio.com/download



Download the modules
--------------------
NPM
---
> npm install express --save(node modules)
> npm install express mongodb mongoose mysql --save
--save : is used to save the version

yarn
----
> yarn add express mongodb mongodb mongoose mysql --save
